# Theme system

## Behavior

- User-selectable **Light**, **Dark**, and **System** (follow `prefers-color-scheme` when System).
- Persist preference in **`localStorage`** under key **`agriq-theme`** (see `src/theme/themeShared.ts`).
- Apply resolved theme to **`document.documentElement`**: toggle class **`dark`**, set **`colorScheme`** style for native controls.

## File roles

- **`themeShared.ts`**: pure helpers (`resolveTheme`, `applyResolvedToDom`, storage read) — no React.
- **`context.ts`**: `createContext` only (keeps Fast Refresh happy with ESLint).
- **`ThemeProvider.tsx`**: state, effects, `matchMedia` subscription when preference is System.
- **`useTheme.ts`**: single hook to read/update preference.

## First paint

- **`index.html`** may include a small inline script that reads `localStorage` and sets `dark` / `color-scheme` before React loads to reduce flash (FOUC).

## UI

- Theme control lives in the **header** (e.g. `ThemeSelect`) with a visible label and/or `aria-label` on the control.
